{"tid":532500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美諜戰升溫 情報部門警告庫什納提防鄧文迪","createTime":"2018-01-18T01:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T04:19:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7599e6f9eb64a8584f2c0f2d74cf4ce6bbbd92be","tid":532500,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"美國對中國的反間諜工作越來越高調，最新曝光的是美籍華人鄧文迪。《華爾街日報》引述美國情報消息<br />\n，指情報人員在2017年初已經向特朗普女婿庫什納提出警告，指鄧文迪可能利用她跟庫什納的關係，獲取中國政府在美國的利益，內地《環球時報》亦有轉載這篇報道。<br />\n<br />\n報道還指，由中國政府控制的一家公司，正透過鄧文迪的影響力，游說美國政府部門，讓他們在白宮附近與建一個公園，公園內會建一座高塔，高度足以清楚監控白宮的外圍，該計劃已經擱置。<br />\n<br />\n鄧文迪的經歷一直是國際焦點，早年移居美國的鄧文迪，在九十年代到香港衛視任職時，認識了國際傳媒大亨梅鐸，兩人在1999年結婚，2013年離婚，西方不少傳媒披露，離婚原因是鄧文迪跟前英國前首相貝理雅，有不尋常關係。<br />\n<br />\n#傳奇女子<br />\n#中美諜戰<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&d=hZ%2Fq%2Fd2VlDcwjyJMHBVxpkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=67cc2676\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/</a>"},{"pid":"181b338209eccc15bba7c3564333cfa5ae54c78f","tid":532500,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"鄧文迪到底有咩吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a598aaafee91d4679d855b47febb695934aad77","tid":532500,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"181b338209eccc15bba7c3564333cfa5ae54c78f","tid":532500,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"鄧文迪到底有咩吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"唔知但真係好撚勁<br />\n可能牀技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5